    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Do not make your wants many, especially if the income for home expenses is limited. Bring your wants within your parents&rsquo; means. The Lord will recognize and <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"387\"></span> commend your unselfish efforts.... Be faithful in that which is least. You will then be in no danger of neglecting greater responsibilities. God&apos;s word declares, &ldquo;He that is faithful in that which is least is faithful also in much.&rdquo;<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 2, 1903\" data-link=\"14068.7593001\">Manuscript 2, 1903</span>.</span></a></sup>",
    "puborder": 1188,
