    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Keep a little money box on the mantel or in some safe place where it can be seen, in which the children can place their offerings for the Lord.... Thus they may be trained for God.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">11<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 128, 1901\" data-link=\"14066.9576001\">Manuscript 128, 1901</span>.</span></a></sup>",
